</taxonomicName>
closest morphological species. A. 
<taxonomicName box="[906,998,1915,1936]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Graptopetalum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="8" pageNumber="167" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="glassii">
